ing downLounge chairs are used as signature furniture pieces in homes offices waiting rooms and.";i:21;s:371:"A direct answer to traditional furnishings perceived by Le Corbusier as obsolete and relic-like the sleek stripped down tubular shapes of the LC1 created a stark contrast to the suffocating wads of padding and upholstery permeating the furniture trends of the timeDesigned in 1928 and soon coming to be regarded as a classic of modern design the chair is notable for the.";i:22;s:59:"Wayfair Lounge Chair Sale - Wayfair Lounge Chair Furniture.";i:23;s:32:"Free Shipping on Orders Over 35.";i:24;s:41:"Shop Furniture Home Décor Cookware More.";i:25;s:36:"Free Shipping on All Orders Over 35.";i:26;s:100:"Double Lounge Chair is a furniture item the player can use together with their spouse to get a buff.";i:27;s:59:"Double Lounge Chair can be purchased at the following shop.";i:28;s:83:"One Double Lounge Chair is required for Gingers A Trip to Starlight Island mission.";i:29;s:96:"Double Lounge Chair can be placed on the ground anywhere inside the players house or their yard.";i:30;s:51:"It takes up 3x3 space and provides no stat bonuses.";i:31;s:37:"Look for three specific measurements.";i:32;s:99:"An authentic Eames Lounge Chair should measure 32 inches from the floor to the top of the headrest.";i:33;s:80:"Many copies will be several inches to 10 or more inches taller than an original.";i:34;s:113:"The front seat edge will be about 15 inches above the floor but note that some copies have that same measurement.";i:35;s:356:"The Eames Lounge Chair and ottoman are furnishings made of molded plywood and leather designed by Charles and Ray Eames for the Herman Miller furniture companyThey are officially titled Eames Lounge 670 and Ottoman 671 and were released in 1956 after years of development by designers it was the first chair that the Eameses designed for a high-end market.";i:36;s:95:"A comfortable chair on which people can sit or lie in order to relax especially outside in hot.";i:37;s:97:"Lounge chair definition a chair designed for lounging as an easy chair chaise longue or recliner.";i:38;s:90:"The Pink Lounge Chair is a furniture block that can be crafted in the furniture workbench.";i:39;s:43:"It was added in the January 29 2021 update.";i:40;s:54:"The Lounge Chair is available from Vitra in two sizes.";i:41;s:55:"With classic dimensions and with new larger dimensions.";i:42;s:177:"Furthermore the various combinations of leather upholstery covers wooden shells and bases are now complemented by a white edition and a black edition with corresponding details.";i:43;s:15:"View talk edit.";i:44;s:63:"The Lounge Chair is a unique decoration available in FarmVille.";i:45;s:57:"The Lounge Chair is a possible reward from a Mystery Box.";i:46;s:6:"V d e.";i:47;s:70:"Fandom Apps Take your favorite fandoms with you and never miss a beat.";}}